arm_group.description:
12 patients with Rett syndrome receiving a daily dose of desipramine correlated with the weight :
From 15 to 25 kg : 50 mg ;
From 26 to 35 kg : 75 mg ;
From 36 to 45 kg : 100 mg ;
> 46 kg : 150 mg.

